snippet: Louisiana State won its first five football games yet dropped another spot in the Associated Press poll this week, prompting concerns in Baton Rouge with a daunting schedule ahead.
abstract: Louisiana State drops another spot in the Associated Press college football poll, despite being 5-0; team faces a daunting schedule ahead.
